Nutrient data for: 45001403, ESSENTIAL EVERYDAY, MEUSLI, MULTI GRAIN CEREAL WITH RAISINS, DATES & ALMONDS, UPC: 041303001547

DEGERMED CORN MEAL, RAISINS, WHOLE BARLEY, WHEAT BRAN, DATES, WHOLE OATS, SUGAR, CONTAINS LESS THAN 2% OF THE FOLLOWING: ALMONDS, RICE, SALT, BARLEY MALT EXTRACT, BROWN SUGAR MOLASSES, CANOLA OIL, SOY LECITHIN. VITAMINS AND MINERALS: VITAMIN C (ASCORBIC ACID), NIACIN (NIACINAMIDE), IRON (FERRIC ORTHOPHOSPHATE), VITAMIN B6 (PYRIDOXINE HYDROCHLORIDE), VITAMIN E (ALPHA TOCOPHEROL ACETATE), ZINC (ZINC OXIDE), FOLIC ACID, VITAMIN A (BETA CAROTENE), VITAMIN B2 (RIBOFLAVIN), VITAMIN B1 (THIAMIN HYDROCHLORIDE), CALCIUM PANTOTHENATE, VITAMIN A PALMITATE, VITAMIN B12 (CYANOCOBALAMIN), VITAMIN D (CHOLECALCIFEROL).
